{"tid":1164380,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"美國總統如認為香港自治情況不足以有別於中華人民共和國，總統有權簽發行政命令中止此法","createTime":"2019-05-21T04:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T13:57:07.000Z","uid":88428,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"16f28f9addbd9da0f8e7dbeb3bd5999e6762c597","tid":1164380,"uid":88428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T04:50:49.000Z","msg":"《美國－香港政策法》（英語：United States&ndash;Hong Kong Policy Act），又稱為《香港關係法》、《美港關係法》，是一部現行的美國國內法，由美國國會在1992年通過的法案。<br />\n<br />\n鑑於在1997年7月1日，英國結束對香港的管治後，香港主權移交成為中華人民共和國轄下的一個特別行政區，美國政府重新釐定對港政策。<br />\n<br />\n美國國會通過此法案承認「香港獨立關稅區」，將香港區別於中國大陸，在一國兩制框架之下，支持香港人權、民主與自治，保障香港生活方式及美資在此國際金融中心、自由港營商。"},{"pid":"c794eb56ab7f9d9550bdb762afbb7adc7c388234","tid":1164380,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:00:03.000Z","msg":"走資啦，望！"},{"pid":"c7792aa71583c39647acadc127da1d69eb840146","tid":1164380,"uid":88428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T05:02:24.000Z","msg":"窮撚冇資<br />\n唔使走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7b627396bf6fee9c1b73d452b3a131d31b6fe7","tid":1164380,"uid":88428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4515689f1adad55a794c4e00c4b9663025cd4c","tid":1164380,"uid":88428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T13:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}